Second largest Conch Cottage  (Dreamsicle model) Open floor plan with high ceilings. L-shaped screen porch. Upgrade with 42" cabinet and flooring. Extended quartz countertops. Monthly fees *$294.75 total fees are shown monthly, however, collected quarterly. What your fees cover: Common area maintenance (lawn, landscape, trees, irrigation.
